            <title><![CDATA[#用刮油食品达到刮油目的是不科学的#【#刮油食品真能刮油吗#[思考]】大鱼大肉吃多了想要“刮刮油”？专家表示，“刮油食品”其实是我们的想象，通过食用一些食品...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%A8%E5%88%AE%E6%B2%B9%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%88%AE%E6%B2%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%A8%E5%88%AE%E6%B2%B9%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%88%AE%E6%B2%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#用刮油食品达到刮油目的是不科学的#</span></a>【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%88%AE%E6%B2%B9%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E7%9C%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%AE%E6%B2%B9%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%88%AE%E6%B2%B9%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E7%9C%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%AE%E6%B2%B9%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#刮油食品真能刮油吗#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】大鱼大肉吃多了想要“刮刮油”？专家表示，“刮油食品”其实是我们的想象，通过食用一些食品来达到“刮油”目的，这也是不科学的，因为脂肪被吃进去后，不会一直存在于肠道之中，很快就会被人体消化吸收。 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4866227395559477" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视频的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/007S2YvRly1hatzmq9q34j31hc0u0aoo.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/PO9YxYRTlx082Wo8WRzW01041200mRAv0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675930865&amp;ssig=D4S%2Bz6saC6&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/lWMJUdpulx082Wo7K8re01041200boGN0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1675930865&amp;ssig=%2BX